  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A small device of your own description emits a sphere of noise cancellation. You have advantage on checks to remain hidden and movement you make that would create sound cannot be heard more than 5 feet away from you. As an action, you can spend a charge extend the effect of this device up to a 10 foot sphere for 1 minute, allowing allied creatures within that range to gain the same benefits.</p>",
